OL,3,CPride of Britain 2024: Meet the
OL,4,Cnominees for Border's Fundraiser of
OL,5,Cthe Year
OL,7,FJim McLelland
OL,9,FJim from Crossmichael near Castle
OL,10,FDouglas lost his first wife, Diane, to
OL,11,Fcancer in 1994 and his second wife,
OL,12,FRuth, to the same disease last year.
OL,14,FHe's raised thousands of pounds to
OL,15,Fgive back to the service which helped
OL,16,Fboth of his wives.
