OL,3,CPride of Britain 2024: Meet the
OL,4,Cnominees for Border's Fundraiser of
OL,5,Cthe Year
OL,7,FHis event One Big Thank You raised
OL,8,F#25,000 earlier this year and involved
OL,9,Fhim running, walking and jogging for
OL,10,F12 hours, matching the standard shift
OL,11,Ftime for NHS staff.
OL,13,FJim said: "When Ruth passed away we
OL,14,Fhad been five weeks at the hospital.
OL,16,F"I could see all the things that
OL,17,Fpeople did, from the cleaners to the
OL,18,Fteachers to the secretaries, to all of
OL,19,Fthe people that are there and all
OL,20,Fgiving a fantastic service and a real
OL,21,Freal feeling of caring.
