OL,3,CPride of Britain 2024: Meet the
OL,4,Cnominees for Border's Fundraiser of
OL,5,Cthe Year
OL,7,F"They'll be there 365 days of the year
OL,8,Flooking after us - it's time we look
OL,9,Fafter them."
OL,11,FBethany Barnes
OL,13,FBethany from Egremont in West Cumbria
OL,14,Fwas diagnosed with osteosarcoma, a
OL,15,Fform of bone cancer, when she was 22-
OL,16,Fyears-old.
OL,18,FShe had her leg amputated as part of
OL,19,Fher treatment and has raised #15,000
OL,20,Ffor bone cancer charities.
