OL,3,CPride of Britain 2024: Meet the
OL,4,Cnominees for Border's Fundraiser of
OL,5,Cthe Year
OL,7,FOn two occasions, Bethany has taken on
OL,8,Fthe challenge of walking the 11km
OL,9,Froute around Ennerdale Water to raise
OL,10,Fmoney and awareness for bone cancer
OL,11,Fcharities.
OL,13,FBethany said she hoped the challege
OL,14,Fwould also inspire others: "There was
OL,15,Fa few people on the walk who got
OL,16,Fthemselves into their own little rut
OL,17,Fin their life.
