OL,3,CPride of Britain 2024: Meet the
OL,4,Cnominees for Border's Fundraiser of
OL,5,Cthe Year
OL,7,F"Just seeing somebody with struggles
OL,8,Flike me doing that walk, gave them a
OL,9,Fkick up the bum to do their own little
OL,10,Fmissions in life and a little bit of
OL,11,Fpositive motivation, which was good."
OL,13,FRhiannon Ridgewell
OL,15,FRhiannon from Carlisle volunteers for
OL,16,FCumbria Wildlife Trust, and has been
OL,17,Fcycling 7km everyday for a year to
OL,18,Fraise money for the charity.
