OL,3,CPride of Britain 2024: Meet the
OL,4,Cnominees for Border's Fundraiser of
OL,5,Cthe Year
OL,7,FShe said she wants to make a
OL,8,Fdifference and inspire others to as
OL,9,Fwell: "I want my children to be able
OL,10,Fto tell people in 30 years that my mum
OL,11,Ftried.
OL,13,F"I tried to do something and everybody
OL,14,Fcan make some difference.
OL,16,F"Everybody can do something and it's
OL,17,Fnot hopeless, you can be positive and
OL,18,Fis not completely overwhelming.
OL,20,F"If everybody does something, we could
OL,21,Fturn this around."
